cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about human parsing, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper proposes a novel method that utilizes a graph pyramid module and mutual learning, which involves training multiple models simultaneously. This suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, since the paper deals with semantic segmentation, which is a common task in computer graphics, it may also belong to cs.CR (Computer Graphics).
